Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.62,0:03:38.73,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那么我们有很多要解决的问题\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}so we have a lot to settle.
