Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.37,0:03:42.01,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}就像我的所有那些长视频一样\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}and just like all my long videos,
