Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.43,0:25:47.84,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}再说一遍 几乎所有列出来的东西都是在去年造好的\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}again, almost everything we're about to list was built within the last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.84,0:25:49.02,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}从Starshopper开始\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}Starting with Starhopper,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.02,0:25:52.26,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}而这是唯一能飞的Starship原型机\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}which is the only Starship prototype to really fly,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.26,0:25:55.81,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}虽然说是为了试飞而制造的 至少飞了两次\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}well on purpose, at least, with two flights,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.81,0:25:59.03,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}一次是20米飞行 另一次是150米飞行\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}a 20-meter hop and a 150-meter hop.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.03,0:26:02.07,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}然后我们看到了全尺寸原型一号机的组装\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}Then we saw the Mark 1 full-scale prototype come together.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.07,0:26:05.69,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}也在那时 SpaceX在 佛罗里达州可可建造了一个类似的原型机\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}At the same time, SpaceX was building a similar prototype in Cocoa, Florida
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.73,0:26:11.53,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这种方式可以让两个不同的团队在友谊赛中研究不同的施工方法\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}as a way for two different teams to work on different methods of construction in a friendly competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.53,0:26:16.47,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}二号机 正如我们所知 现在遗弃在那里\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}Mark 2, as it was known, has since been abandoned and is still just hanging out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.47,0:26:22.66,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}然后我们在2019年底看到两个团队合理完成并测试了一号原型机\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}Then we saw the two teams come together at the end of 2019 to finish and test the Mark 1 prototype,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.66,0:26:24.06,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}测试失败了\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}which failed when testing,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.06,0:26:28.11,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}某种程度上这个失败是能预测到的 因为他们开始了下一个原型机的制造\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}as was kind of expected because they were already working on the next one,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.11,0:26:29.89,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这个被称为序列号1(SN1)\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}which would be called SN1,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.22,0:26:33.57,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这时他们开始把命名的方式从几号机改成序列号几\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}and that's when they switched from the Mark to Serial Number nomenclature.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.10,0:26:38.56,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}在这段时间 已经有三个非全尺寸的试验品对焊接工艺进行了测试\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}There's been three subscale pressure test articles that have tested the welds
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.57,0:26:42.62,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}以及在低温的情况下耐压的能力\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}and the ability to hold pressure at cryogenic temperatures around this time, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.42,0:26:44.70,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}他们测试了SN1\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}They tested SN1,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.70,0:26:47.53,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}某种程度上是内爆了 当它的底部掉下来时\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}which kind of imploded when its bottom fell off.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.53,0:26:52.93,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}然后我们看到了SN3 因为不正确的测试程序 也失败了\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}Then we have SN3, which also failed due to improper testing procedures.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.93,0:26:54.45,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}而且 正在这个视频制作的时候\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}And, as of the making of this video,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.45,0:26:59.61,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}SN4已经完成 而SN5则是大步向前\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}SN4 is already complete and SN5 is well on its way.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.61,0:27:04.37,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}如果我不断地尝试通过他们制造的新部件来更新这个愚蠢的动画\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}And if I keep trying to update this stupid animation with all the new parts they're making,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.37,0:27:06.03,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这个视频永远都做不出来\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}this video will never come out,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.03,0:27:09.35,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}因为他们做这些东西实在是太快了\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}because they're just making them so quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.35,0:27:12.68,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}因此 换句话说 SpaceX已经造好并炸毁了\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}So in other words, SpaceX has built and blown up
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.92,0:27:19.75,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}比SLS 3倍多的储罐 在过去的半年里\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}three times more tanks in the last six months than SLS has built in the last six years.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.38,0:27:27.90,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}而这正是我们看到的在制造 测试和整体理念的巨大的差异\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}And this is where we see the massive, massive differences in the building, testing, and overall philosophies.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.50,0:27:30.16,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}再仔细研究下这里\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}Time to dig into this for a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.93,0:27:41.35,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你现在也许已经知道这里面的设计理念差异\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}By now you've already probably got a really good sense of the design differences and philosophies
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.56,0:27:44.61,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}只要看看这两个项目发展的历史\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}just by seeing how these two programs have developed over time.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.16,0:27:50.15,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但是还有几件事真的能看出他们之间的巨大区别\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}But there's a few things that really, really drill in just how different they truly are.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.15,0:27:53.25,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那么 让我们从NASA的角度来看看\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}So let's start by putting ourselves in NASA's shoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.25,0:27:55.05,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}NASA 被政府资助的机构\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}NASA, being government funded,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.05,0:27:59.92,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}必须和私人赞助的私人公司有很多不同\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}has to do things quite a lot differently than a private company with private funding,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.92,0:28:04.97,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但这之中最关键的事情也许是他们真的不能冒很大的险\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}but perhaps the biggest thing they can't really do is take big risks.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.97,0:28:08.73,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}当他们在建造一些巨大 复杂 且有野心的项目类似SLS这样的\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}When building something as massive, complex and ambitious as SLS,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.73,0:28:11.88,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你就真的需要说明几乎所有的东西\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}you really need to account for absolutely everything
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.92,0:28:14.64,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}在你给承包商发出指令之前\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}before you start sending out the instructions to the contractors.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.02,0:28:21.80,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}如果你告诉你的承包商开始建造某个东西 而在计划中有了新的变化\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}If you start telling contractors to start building something and then something changes in the plan,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.80,0:28:23.75,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}所有(改变前进行)的工作都将是徒劳的\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}all of that work is for naught.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.75,0:28:28.50,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}而当你有着几十个承包商和若干公务员的时候 加剧了这种情况\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}And this compounds when you have dozens of contractors and government supporting employees
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.62,0:28:32.09,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}他们都依赖于对方及时地完成自己的那部分工作\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}all relying on each other to have their parts done on time.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.53,0:28:35.26,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}想象一下一个关键组件延迟了一年\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}Imagine if a key part gets delayed a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.26,0:28:39.30,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}支持这个系统的公务员该怎么办\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}What are the government employees supporting that system supposed to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.30,0:28:43.27,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你不能把他们解雇一年再让他们回来为项目工作吧\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}You can't just lay them off for a year and then bring them back onto the project,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.27,0:28:44.85,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}他们会去找新的工作\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}they're gonna go find new work.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.85,0:28:47.28,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你不能给他们重新分配别的事干\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}You can't really reassign them to something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.28,0:28:52.53,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不像是推进系统工程师现在可以研究别的火箭去了\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}It's not like a propulsion engineer is now just going to move over to the other rocket
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.54,0:28:54.23,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}而这个火箭也是NASA现在正在研制的\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}NASA is currently working on.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.69,0:29:02.29,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}在运行这种规模的项目时 每年都有很多固有的沉没成本\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}There's a lot of inherent costs per year that are sunk costs in running a program of this scale.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.29,0:29:05.47,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}所以 尽管它本来就风险小 效率低\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}So, although it's inherently less risky and inefficient,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.47,0:29:11.32,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但对于多个承包商还是有个安全的网络 和遍布全国的太空中心\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}there's also a safety net for having multiple contractors and space centers spread throughout the country,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.61,0:29:15.26,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这些都会更加吸引国会\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}which massively helps make it more appealing to congress.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.26,0:29:17.81,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}所以 尽管它是低效的\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}So, although it is inefficient,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.23,0:29:22.46,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}它至少确保了项目的生存性 并且让它能持续地得到资助\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}it at least does help ensure the program survival and that it continues to be funded.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.64,0:29:28.77,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}当你发现欧罗巴快船那事儿写进法律的时候 你就会发现这话太对了\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}And this is especially true when you realize that it's written into law that the Europa Clipper,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.77,0:29:34.44,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这个访问土星的卫星 土卫二欧罗巴的探测器 被立法授权了要使用SLS进行发射\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}a probe to Jupiter's moon, Europa, is legally mandated to fly on SLS.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.44,0:29:36.68,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}关于这事儿最疯狂的地方也许在于\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}And perhaps most nutty about that fact is
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.77,0:29:40.48,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是项目得到了2.5亿美元的资助\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}that $250 million has been added to the program
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.54,0:29:45.69,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}因为直到至少2025年都不会有SLS火箭\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}because there won't be an SLS rocket until at least 2025,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.69,0:29:49.04,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}尽管这个探测器2023年就造好了\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}despite the probe being ready by 2023.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.60,0:29:55.28,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但是长远来看 这个法案能够确保SLS这个项目持续前进并得到资助\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}But in the long run, this law did help keep a program moving forward and being funded
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.29,0:29:59.84,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}特别是在这种不断换届的政府 充满变化的时代之下\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}during what could be very uncertain times with changing administrations.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.04,0:30:02.39,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}显然现在这样很不理想\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}Now this obviously isn't ideal at all,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.39,0:30:05.79,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但如果你担心项目的生存能力\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}but if you're worried about program survivability
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.05,0:30:12.15,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}同时不只是让你的整个视野范围每四或八年就翻个180度\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}and not just having your entire vision shift 180 degrees every four to eight years,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.15,0:30:17.56,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}无论好坏 这样做事就是游戏规则的一部分\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}doing things like this is just kinda part of the game, for better or worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.84,0:30:22.37,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但是别忘了 NASA的预算只有国家预算的0.5%\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}But don't forget, NASA's budget is only about half a percent of our national budget,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.37,0:30:26.73,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}而载人航天项目甚至不到这其中的一半\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}and the human space flight programs aren't even half of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.73,0:30:33.17,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}因此 在一般情况下 建造SLS的主要理念是提前计划 并减小风险\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}So in general, the primary philosophy of building SLS is to plan ahead and take little risks,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.17,0:30:36.03,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}因为实在没有多少空间容许失败\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}because there really isn't much room to fail
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.03,0:30:40.92,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}在这种情况下 你必须向纳税人回答为什么他们的钱灰飞烟灭了\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}when you have to answer to the taxpayers why their money literally went up in smoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.98,0:30:42.81,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}现在再对比下Starship\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}Now compare this to Starship.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.81,0:30:47.43,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Starship的发展得到的成果真的就是与它的从头开始这点密切相关\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}Starship development is literally about as blank slate as it gets.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.43,0:30:50.67,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}SpaceX开始的时候不仅没有详细的蓝图\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}SpaceX started not with detailed blueprints,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.67,0:30:55.39,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}而且真的就是从如何提问开始的\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}but quite literally started by just learning what questions to ask
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.76,0:30:59.40,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}如何框住他们火箭性能的需求\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}and how to frame the constraints of what their vehicle should do.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.68,0:31:03.27,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}SpaceX最终得到了两个主要目标\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}SpaceX seems to have wound up on two main objectives.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.27,0:31:04.97,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}一个是充分且迅速的重复使用\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}Be fully and rapidly reusable,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.14,0:31:10.97,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}另一个则是有着足够大的运载能力能让人类登陆其他天体\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}and have a capability large enough to be useful in getting humans onto other celestial bodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.72,0:31:15.98,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这才是它的需求 然后倒着来设计\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}That's really about it, and then start to work backwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.98,0:31:19.00,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}下一个能够回答这个问题的明确的项目是\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}The next most pinned down item that helps to answer
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.02,0:31:24.00,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}研发一个高效且能大量重复使用的发动机\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}that question is developing an engine that is efficient and massively reusable.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.33,0:31:27.28,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}就像我那个讨论了SpaceX猛禽发动机的视频\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}Like I talked about in my video about SpaceX's Raptor engine,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.28,0:31:30.51,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}一个甲烷驱动的全流量分级燃烧循环发动机\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}a methane powered full-flow staged combustion cycle engine,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.51,0:31:33.21,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}能够完美地达到那些目标\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}fits the needs of those goals perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.21,0:31:36.68,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}从那里开始 整个事情就像是一个巨大的游乐场一样\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}From there on, the whole thing is pretty much just a giant playground.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.68,0:31:42.02,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}因此 当我们看到从碳纤维到不锈钢的突然而出人意料的转折时\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}Hence, when we saw the sudden and unexpected pivot from carbon fiber to stainless steel,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.02,0:31:46.66,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你就会知道只是开始飞行这件事对于SpaceX而言是多么重要\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}you get a sense of just how important it is for SpaceX to just start flying
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.86,0:31:49.36,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这样他们才有一个可以迭代的起点\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}so they have a starting point to iterate on
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.66,0:31:54.20,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这也就是马一龙解释说为什么这个转变是如此的重要\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}when you hear Elon explain why it was so important to make the switch.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.24,0:31:56.04,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4} - 以一般方法\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}- Taking the general approach of,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.33,0:31:59.60,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}如如果设计花费的时间太长 那么它就是错误的\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}if a design is taking too long, the design is wrong,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.60,0:32:03.67,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}因此 设计时必须进行修改 以加快进度\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}and therefore the design must be modified to accelerate progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.67,0:32:05.19,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}- 对\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}- Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.19,0:32:09.66,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4} - 坚持设计是一个在高级的研发所作出的最基本的错误\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}- One of the most fundamental errors made in advanced development is to stick to a design
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.67,0:32:14.80,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}即便这只是一个过于复杂而不去尝试通过减少过程和部件(来简化它)的问题\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}even when it is very complicated and to not strive to delete parts and processes.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.69,0:32:16.63,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这是非常重要的\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}It's incredibly important.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.63,0:32:22.83,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}所以这就是为什么改用钢 是因为(制造)先进的碳纤维耗时太长\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}So this is why the switch to steel was because the advanced carbon fiber was taking too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.83,0:32:26.12,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这就是为什么我们在那里看到了那么多随机性的事件\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}This is why we're seeing so many random things happening down there
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.13,0:32:28.69,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}也就是德克萨斯州 博卡奇卡 Starship的研发中\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}at Boca Chica, Texas with the development of Starship.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.03,0:32:33.73,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这就是为什么再去问他们未来的计划都有点蠢了\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}It's why it's kind of silly to even bother asking about future plans anymore,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.73,0:32:37.16,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}当然了 我也是这个愚蠢的分子之一(笑)\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}which of course I'm as guilty of as anyone. (chuckles)
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.16,0:32:41.35,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}因为所有的东西都取决于现阶段的情况\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}Because everything depends on what's going to happen with the current step,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.35,0:32:47.63,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}以后的发展将会取决于前一步的结果 等等\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}and the step in development after that will be based on the results of the previous step and etc etc.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.63,0:32:50.96,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这个理念类似于敏捷建模\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}It's a similar philosophy to something known as the agile model
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.96,0:32:53.22,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这是软件开发的标准\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}which is standard in software development,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.38,0:32:56.75,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这很合理 因为马一龙原本的背景是软件\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}which makes sense because of Elon's original background in software.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.94,0:33:01.53,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}基本上 你在第一步完成之前不需要进行第二步的工作\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}Basically, you don't work on step two until step one is done.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.53,0:33:06.78,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}任何提前的规划可能会导致你必须要撤回之前所做的\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}Planning ahead any further and you're very likely going to have to just undo work.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.78,0:33:10.41,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那么这与SLS的理念完全相反\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}Now this is quite literally the opposite of SLS,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.41,0:33:13.25,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}SLS的所有组成都需要一个确切的计划\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}where everything needs to have an exact plan
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.25,0:33:17.24,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}因为 如果你的火箭造得比蓝图上的要短3米\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}because, if you end up building the rocket three meters shorter than the blueprints,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.39,0:33:20.35,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}突然间 你的整个地面支持系统也要进行更改了\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}all of a sudden your entire ground support system will change too,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.56,0:33:26.52,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}顺便说一句 基本上SLS和它的移动发射塔已经发生了很多这样的事情\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}and by the way, pretty much this exact thing has basically happened with SLS and its mobile launch tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.52,0:33:29.74,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但是 Starship的所有东西还在考虑当中\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}But everything for Starship is still on the table at the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.74,0:33:35.98,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我是指 我真的是看到他们是围着火箭造工厂 而不是反过来\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}I mean, we're literally seeing them build a factory around a rocket instead of vice versa.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.98,0:33:38.49,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}坦率地说 这是非常危险的\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}And frankly, this is pretty risky.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.49,0:33:40.94,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但它也很容易做的\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}But it's also much easier to do,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.94,0:33:44.61,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}因为SpaceX就是如此垂直整合的\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}because SpaceX is so vertically integrated,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.61,0:33:50.61,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这意味着在决策的变化并不会有其他更传统的方法产生的连锁反应大\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}meaning changes in decisions don't have nearly as big of a ripple effect as the other, more traditional methods.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.61,0:33:54.29,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但正如我们所知道的那样 会有更多的设备出现失败\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}But just know, we will see more hardware fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.29,0:33:58.77,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我们会看到一些失利 我们还有可能看到一些爆炸\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}We will see some setbacks, we will likely see explosions.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.77,0:34:02.38,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但是 它和SLS不一样 不仅是失败对它影响不大\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}But, unlike SLS, not only is it okay to fail,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.38,0:34:09.22,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}而且这种成败皆可的预期 也可以作为一种方法来廉价快速地学习并建造原型机\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}it's halfway expected as a way to learn and prototype with lower cost and greater speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.22,0:34:12.62,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}马一龙总是这么说过\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}Elon has said over and over in some way or another,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.06,0:34:21.39,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这与苏联的设计理念非常类似\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}This is very similar to the Soviet Union's design philosophy.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.69,0:34:24.91,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}基本上 尽可能廉价地建造某个事物\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}Basically, build something as cheap as possible,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.91,0:34:26.83,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}测试一下 如果它炸毁\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}test it out, if it blows up,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.83,0:34:30.72,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}看看哪里出了问题 做出改进 再重复这一过程\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}see what went wrong, make improvements, repeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.72,0:34:35.14,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这在早期的太空竞赛当中肯定是帮了他们一把\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}And it definitely gave them a leg up in the space race during early development.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.14,0:34:38.35,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}所以说要如果炸毁了那个一个月内造好的火箭\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}So say you blow up a rocket that you built in a month,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.35,0:34:39.89,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}好吧 从中吸取教训\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}oh well, learn from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.21,0:34:46.45,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}SpaceX建造另一枚火箭的速度 会比NASA加满燃料并点火测试一次SLS的速度更快\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}SpaceX will build another rocket in less time than it'll take NASA to fuel up and test fire the SLS once.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.09,0:34:51.37,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这就是设计理念中的巨大区别\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}And that's just simply a huge, huge difference in philosophies.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.45,0:35:01.69,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}好吧 是时候把这俩火箭摞起来并排比比\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}Okay, I think it's time we really stack these rockets up side by side to help figure out
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.85,0:35:05.78,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这样才能做到真正的对比\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}just how they really compare when we look at their nuts and bolts.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.97,0:35:07.81,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我们已经谈过了这两种火箭的尺寸\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}We've already touched on each vehicle's dimensions,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.81,0:35:10.12,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这就是它们在屏幕上的样子\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}so here they are again on screen.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.12,0:35:13.41,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}现在 我们只会比较每个火箭的最初版本\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}For now, we'll compare some initial builds of each rocket,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.41,0:35:20.26,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}因此这是SLS Block 1和Block 1B和现在Starship的粗糙版\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}so the Block 1 and Block 1B of SLS and the rough-ish version of Starship as it currently stands.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.26,0:35:23.65,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但可以肯定的是 Starship会改变很多(笑)\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}But definitely keep in mind that Starship will change (chuckles) a lot,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.65,0:35:26.90,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}每造一个 几乎都会变几十处\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}pretty much every time one gets built for at least the first dozen or two.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.90,0:35:31.55,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但是如果Block 1B上线 SLS还可以改变一点\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}But SLS could also change a bit too if Block 1B goes online.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.55,0:35:32.61,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}既然说到这儿了\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}But while we're at it,
